User Stories

1. As a User, I need the ability to create an account, so that I can login. [X]
2. As a User, I need the ability to access my profile, so that I can update it. [X]

3. As a Sponsor, I need to specify the documents that I need, so that the students can supply them. [X]
4. As a Sponsor, I need the ability to access the documents submitted by a student, so I can approve them. [X]

5. As a Facilitator, I need to assign a Sponsor to a Student. [X]
6. As a Student, I need to submit the required documents, so the Sponsor can see them.[X]

7.1 As an Employer, I need the ability to create a job, so the Facilitator can see it. [X]
7.2 As a Facilitator, I need the ability to assign a job, so the student can see it. [X]

8. As a Student, I need to see the job assigned to me, so that I can submit the required documents. [X]
9. As an Employer, I need the ability to access the documents submitted, so I can review them. []